title: Ready Steady Wiggle
description: Join Emma, Lachy, Simon and Anthony, along with their wiggly friends, on musical adventures in Wiggle Town.

title: Season 3, Episode 13
description: The Wiggles have been so busy that they have forgotten to eat! They each have a healthy snack and then decide to check on their wiggly friends to see if they might be hungry too.

title: Season 3, Episode 12
description: It's been raining and Emma was hoping to see a rainbow but can't find one. It's decided she'll draw one instead, so she calls on her wiggly friends to help her find pencils in all different colours.

title: Season 3, Episode 11
description: Emma wants to read the other Wiggles a book, but she can't find her glasses! They all try and help to find them, but eventually discover that Lachy's forgetfulness is part of the problem.

title: Season 3, Episode 10
description: Lachy's been making a vase for the other Wiggles, but accidentally drops it causing it to break. Luckily, when Captain Feathersword sees what happens and that Lachy is upset he comes to the rescue!

title: Season 3, Episode 9
description: It's Musical Instrument Day in Wiggle Town and each of The Wiggles have a different instrument and decide to play them all together. Its then time for a wiggly jam session with all their friends.

title: Season 3, Episode 8
description: It's Captain Feathersword's birthday and he's organised a party to celebrate. The Wiggles and friends are all invited, but panic sets in when the party is due to start and they still haven't arrived.

title: Season 3, Episode 7
description: The Wiggles are feeling hungry and so want to make a fruit salad. There's just one problem, they don't have any fruit! It's decided that Anthony will visit their friends to see if they can help.

title: Season 3, Episode 6
description: It's cold outside and The Wiggles have their cold weather outfits on to keep warm. In the distance they hear teeth chattering so decide to investigate to find out who it could be and if they can help.

title: Season 3, Episode 5
description: Lachy has been busy baking scones for The Wiggles and their friends. Anthony is excited to have one, but before he can, he must make sure his hands are clean!

title: Season 3, Episode 4
description: Emma, Samuel and Bok are looking in the mirror to see what they can see and decide to draw self-portraits.

title: Jandal Burn
description: Life is a crack-up for best mates Puku the kiwi and Kev the kiwifruit. They work together in a jandal shop in the small town of Pikelet, New Zealand where every day brings new surprises.

title: Season 1, Episode 1
description: Puku refuses to do her breakfast dishes and comes home from work to find that her yucky old cereal is alive and sassy.

title: Season 1, Episode 2
description: Puku declares it "Prank Day" and loves making Kev jump with her sneaky pranking. Will Kev get her back with the ultimate prank?

title: Season 1, Episode 3
description: Kev is starstruck when Puku's famous rugby playing brother Hohepa comes to visit - until he learns the shocking truth about him.

title: Season 1, Episode 4
description: When a customer asks for an extra large jandal size, Puku is forced to go into the creepy back room to get it - and finds she's not alone.

title: Season 1, Episode 5
description: When their boss Tony leaves his new 3-D printer in the jandal shop Puku and Kev can't resist printing themselves some cool new stuff.

title: Season 1, Episode 6
description: Kev and Puku think it must be magic when an awesome new chair appears to replace their broken one.

title: Season 1, Episode 7
description: Puku and Kev are scared of a bully at the park until they find that the spray-painting bully has a bully of his own.

title: Season 1, Episode 8
description: When Kev gets the high score on his favourite video game it goes to his head. But will someone else get a higher score?

title: Season 1, Episode 9
description: When Kev and Puku upload their new show to the internet they attract the attention of a troll who just happens to live under a bridge.

title: Season 1, Episode 10
description: Tony the boss sees that jandal sales are down and asks Puku and Kev to make a commercial for the shop with him as the star.
